<plot>Zombies. Shambling scourge of the modern world? Or just a little misunderstood? If in doubt, check out Guy's Guide To Zombies, the definitive A to Z guide to living with the dead! Guy's Guide is a parody of 1950's public safety films which quietly pokes fun at the current international climate of irrational fear.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?225499</url></doc>
